flowchart TD
    Sensor[Physical Sensor\nThermistor / Flow Meter / Contact] --> ADC[ADC Sampling\nFixed sample rate]
    ADC --> Buffer[Ring buffer\nIn device memory]
    Buffer --> Filter[Noise filter\nMoving average / median]
    Filter --> Outlier{Outlier detected?}
    Outlier -->|Yes| Discard[Discard reading\nlog fault counter]
    Outlier -->|No| Calibrate[Apply calibration curve\nRaw → physical unit]
    Calibrate --> Feature[Feature extraction\nMin / max / rate-of-change]
    Feature --> Serialise[Serialise payload\nJSON / Protobuf]
    Serialise --> Dedup{Already acknowledged?}
    Dedup -->|Yes| Drop[Drop duplicate]
    Dedup -->|No| Publish[Publish over MQTT\nto local broker]
    Publish --> Broker[Local MQTT broker]
    Broker --> Bridge[Cloud bridge\nTLS connection]
    Bridge --> Ingest[Cloud ingestion service]
    Ingest --> TSDB[(Time-series database)]
    Ingest --> Stream[Stream processor\nKinesis / Kafka]
